 <br />\n以下轉貼 @Taiwan in the US （<a href=\"https://pse.is/RXDF2）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2FRXDF2%EF%BC%89&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=5c40f6a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/RXDF2）</a><br />\n駐美代表處政治組長趙怡翔臉書也有很詳盡的介紹（<a href=\"https://pse.is/R3EGG）\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpse.is%2FR3EGG%EF%BC%89&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=3a3e2eff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pse.is/R3EGG）</a><br />\n <br />\n🔗 相關推文在這邊，大家快去轉推支持👇，不要忘記加上這些hashtag喔<br />\n#TweetforTaiwan #TaiwanModel #TaiwanCanHelp<br />\n <br />\n1⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256208471869083648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256208471869083648&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=777afc7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256208471869083648&h=c5c044fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256208471869083648</a><br />\n2⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256212662821756931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256212662821756931&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=d021c3c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256212662821756931&h=0eba4c3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256212662821756931</a><br />\n3⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256215756578140160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256215756578140160&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=83037483\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256215756578140160&h=a5e280db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256215756578140160</a><br />\n4⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256226173450846209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256226173450846209&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=f1371db1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256226173450846209&h=6aba325e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256226173450846209</a><br />\n5⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256273239749406720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256273239749406720&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=a81ec61c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256273239749406720&h=a9bdd6cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256273239749406720</a><br />\n6⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256283538481086466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256283538481086466&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=acd057b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FState_IO%2Fstatus%2F1256283538481086466&h=9f8df24f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/State_IO/status/1256283538481086466</a><br />\n7⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/USUN/status/1256229953198227456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSUN%2Fstatus%2F1256229953198227456&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=2da2adfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSUN%2Fstatus%2F1256229953198227456&h=b079bf6e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/USUN/status/1256229953198227456</a><br />\n8⃣ <a href=\"http://twitter.com/USMission2ASEAN/status/1256040773314842624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSMission2ASEAN%2Fstatus%2F1256040773314842624&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw15vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=1b36fdc0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUSMission2ASEAN%2Fstatus%2F1256040773314842624&h=8c68b3c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/USMission2ASEAN/status/1256040773314842624</a><br />\n   <br />\n對此，在國內仍然不能使用推特的中國，他們的官方代表們直接在推特上開嗆啦！<br />\n <br />\n中國駐聯合國代表團推文說：台灣問題早在聯大2758號決議案決定，強烈反對台灣參與世衛，而且這是干涉中國內政的行為，美國是在為沒有妥善回應COVID-19推卸責任！<br />\n <br />\n🔺 簡評１：<br />\nErrrr，先前中共外交部發言人赵立坚試圖將病毒來源講是美國刻意傳播，結果美國國務院召見中國大使表達抗議。這回，中國駐聯合國代表又繼續戰狼外交，我們來看看接下來會發生什麼事。<br />\n <br />\n對了，聯合國大會2758號決議的內容是：「中華人民共和國的代表在聯合國當中代表中國，並把蔣介石的代表從聯合國及所有相關組織當中驅逐出去。」這決議跟台灣問題沒有什麼關聯呢。<br />\n <br />\n再說，不管美國怎麼對待台灣都是美國內政的範圍呀！中國（PRC）從來沒有統治過台灣，每次在那邊喊干涉內政實在是很好笑啊！<br />\n <br />\n🔺 簡評２：<br />\n這大概是國務院在台灣與聯合國相關議題上，歷來最直接也最積極的一次表態，還發起了轉推的行動！！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4f19c4b8473c16dc9bbc2f30526c7f8700d86243","tid":1997817,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:23:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1b51030d5a2adaff2b1caa5b49dd3ad801a6e4cc","tid":1997817,"uid":237465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"immensely support"},{"pid":"ed9b6b47155a470281b2cf031863089c3a023fee","tid":1997817,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:15:03.000Z","msg":"香港人幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c5a76c312b5bd4afceb39d70d702acdc609359","tid":1997817,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:19:14.000Z","msg":"push and rt"},{"pid":"07a4e9cffe18b39715e5425af7382d03c7f99dad","tid":1997817,"uid":17331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"369316d650cf5c09417050f528ca4f101a3b066b","tid":1997817,"uid":213037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T14:43: